reviewText: It was amazing watching this. Like most people I liked Jeff more than Matt (as they addressed in the interviews), but Matt's interview was my favorite. I do highly recommend this DVD set.

Bought this thinking it would give me a better look/understanding of the hardys and it somewhat delivered that. For the most part the interviews are in depth and great but they are old interviews and everything is dated. Not a the best buy i've ever made but not the worst either.
This is very interesting. Learned some stuff about the Matt and Jeff Hardy that I did not know before.
These videos are interesting but I don't know if I will let my son watch them till he gets older because of the language.  Thanks for the quick delivery I have enjoyed watching them.
